WEBVTT

00:21.320 --> 00:26.430
[2009]

00:29.030 --> 00:29.640
Jiang,

00:30.550 --> 00:32.030
go over these two cases.

00:38.470 --> 00:40.350
These days, not many young people

00:40.350 --> 00:41.750
are into pocket watches.

00:42.620 --> 00:44.110
This is quite an antique.

00:44.920 --> 00:45.840
Don't stay up too late.

00:45.840 --> 00:46.320
Okay.

02:15.820 --> 02:21.540
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

02:21.850 --> 02:24.220
[Episode 6]

02:26.840 --> 02:28.120
Let me see.

02:29.800 --> 02:30.800
What was the name?

02:33.360 --> 02:34.079
It was...

02:36.590 --> 02:37.430
Li Neng.

02:47.560 --> 02:50.190
[Intake Officer: Jiang Cheng,
Fang Hongcheng]

03:03.690 --> 03:04.880
I admit

03:05.620 --> 03:07.480
you've got quite an imagination.

03:07.750 --> 03:09.870
But police work relies on evidence.

03:10.170 --> 03:11.570
Do you have any evidence?

04:33.760 --> 04:39.490
[To Jiang Cheng]

05:26.560 --> 05:31.320
[Jiang Hansheng]

05:31.430 --> 05:32.360
Sorry,

05:32.870 --> 05:35.870
the number you dialed
cannot be reached at the moment.

05:54.510 --> 05:56.450
Hello, Criminal Investigation Brigade,
Nancheng Branch.

05:56.450 --> 05:58.250
Hello, is Zhou Jin there?

05:58.640 --> 06:00.690
Zhou Jin? Zhou Jin went home.

06:01.860 --> 06:03.260
Is this Professor Jiang?

06:04.070 --> 06:04.700
Yes.

06:05.870 --> 06:07.350
Zhou Jin left a while ago.

06:07.380 --> 06:09.180
Maybe you can try her cell phone.

06:10.510 --> 06:10.950
Okay.

06:11.510 --> 06:12.110
Thank you.

06:27.390 --> 06:28.040
Hansheng.

06:29.390 --> 06:30.070
Sir.

06:31.300 --> 06:32.500
Do you need anything?

06:35.159 --> 06:36.690
I want to look into someone.

06:37.270 --> 06:38.800
Who do you want to look into?

06:40.950 --> 06:41.680
Jiang Cheng.

06:54.370 --> 06:55.170
Where are you?

06:55.950 --> 06:57.270
Do you want me to pick you up?

06:57.270 --> 06:58.070
I'm at home.

06:59.260 --> 07:00.040
My own home.

07:00.830 --> 07:01.920
I wanted to grab something,

07:01.920 --> 07:02.830
so I came back.

07:04.230 --> 07:05.160
Jiang Hansheng.

07:05.930 --> 07:06.480
Okay.

07:18.070 --> 07:18.600
Zhou Jin.

07:19.870 --> 07:20.750
Do you like me?

07:24.720 --> 07:25.480
I had

07:26.240 --> 07:27.750
a boyfriend

07:27.750 --> 07:28.870
for many years.

07:29.510 --> 07:31.240
That was Jiang Cheng, right?

07:31.920 --> 07:33.270
I warned you before,

07:33.270 --> 07:34.930
and I'm telling you again now.

07:35.720 --> 07:36.950
Stay away from me.

07:37.730 --> 07:38.320
Zhou Jin.

07:39.380 --> 07:40.380
You lost a button.

07:43.220 --> 07:45.020
I don't even know how it came off.

07:58.510 --> 07:59.440
Why are you here?

08:02.510 --> 08:03.710
Why did you come here?

08:05.320 --> 08:06.980
Do you not like living with me?

08:11.410 --> 08:11.940
No.

08:13.310 --> 08:14.970
I came back to get some things.

08:21.000 --> 08:22.530
What happened to your face?

08:24.640 --> 08:26.220
I was at the playground today.

08:26.220 --> 08:27.360
I was hit by a ball.

08:37.320 --> 08:38.580
Let's go inside first.

08:39.730 --> 08:40.270
Let's go.

08:48.570 --> 08:49.970
That's me and my brother.

08:54.930 --> 08:55.640
Have a seat.

09:08.750 --> 09:09.600
Watch some TV.

09:10.440 --> 09:11.440
I'm gonna pack some things.

09:11.440 --> 09:12.440
I'll be done soon.

09:12.720 --> 09:13.510
Then we can

09:14.170 --> 09:15.170
go home together.

09:28.300 --> 09:29.210
What...

09:29.560 --> 09:31.210
book were you just reading?

09:32.590 --> 09:33.790
The Lord of the Rings.

09:47.180 --> 09:48.230
I'll be quick.

09:51.610 --> 09:52.370
Zhou Jin.

10:01.120 --> 10:02.180
when I married you,

10:03.360 --> 10:05.220
was that taking advantage of you?

10:14.450 --> 10:15.380
Of course not.

10:17.830 --> 10:18.880
I married you

10:20.600 --> 10:22.060
because you can hold me up.

10:23.720 --> 10:24.920
You make me feel safe.

10:30.480 --> 10:31.030
Zhou Jin.

10:35.030 --> 10:35.840
You can try.

10:36.960 --> 10:37.800
Try what?

10:40.150 --> 10:41.480
Falling in love with me.

10:55.000 --> 10:55.760
Help me move.

10:56.630 --> 10:57.240
Today.

10:58.390 --> 11:00.120
Move everything to your place.

11:01.460 --> 11:02.030
Okay.

11:02.960 --> 11:03.760
I'll help you.

11:32.630 --> 11:33.430
What's wrong?

11:34.150 --> 11:35.480
You want to take it back?

11:37.160 --> 11:38.760
You can wear it as a necklace.

11:39.870 --> 11:41.260
I run around every day,

11:41.780 --> 11:42.810
what if I lose it?

11:49.240 --> 11:50.240
Whatever you say.

11:50.720 --> 11:51.720
Whatever you say.

12:05.520 --> 12:06.660
[Dan]

12:10.670 --> 12:11.270
Dan.

12:11.840 --> 12:12.390
Zhou Jin,

12:12.790 --> 12:14.320
you're getting suspended.

12:14.920 --> 12:15.590
Why?

12:17.600 --> 12:18.530
On what grounds?

12:19.080 --> 12:20.720
There's a last-minute meeting today.

12:20.720 --> 12:21.720
In the meeting,

12:21.720 --> 12:24.240
they said during your interrogation
of Lai Zhengtian,

12:24.240 --> 12:25.040
you engaged in

12:25.200 --> 12:25.870
suggestive questioning,

12:25.870 --> 12:27.930
and you coerced him into confessing.

12:28.150 --> 12:31.000
As for whether Lai Zhengtian
filed the complaint himself,

12:31.000 --> 12:32.320
or someone from the inside reported it,

12:32.320 --> 12:33.550
we don't know yet.

12:33.880 --> 12:35.670
But I have to say,

12:35.670 --> 12:37.080
Chief Tan is really reliable.

12:37.080 --> 12:38.240
As soon as this happened,

12:38.240 --> 12:39.390
he went straight to the bureau,

12:39.390 --> 12:42.100
saying it was him
who let you join the interrogation,

12:42.100 --> 12:43.730
and that the responsibility lies with him.

12:43.730 --> 12:44.480
But the problem is,

12:44.480 --> 12:46.340
I didn't violate any rules at all.

12:46.840 --> 12:48.040
Wasn't there a video recording?

12:48.040 --> 12:49.640
They can see it very clearly.

12:50.030 --> 12:51.510
Yes, very clearly.

12:51.510 --> 12:53.260
You were too close to Lai Zhengtian.

12:53.260 --> 12:54.750
It was both
against regulations and dangerous.

12:54.750 --> 12:56.030
And you ended up getting hurt.

12:56.030 --> 12:57.600
Anyway, the decision is

12:57.780 --> 12:58.980
to suspend your work.

12:59.240 --> 13:00.600
As for the penalty,

13:01.150 --> 13:03.610
we'll have to wait
for the official results.

13:04.200 --> 13:05.200
For how many days?

13:05.680 --> 13:07.030
It depends on how they classify it.

13:07.030 --> 13:08.430
Just wait for the notice.

13:09.030 --> 13:10.230
Is this a suspension?

13:10.520 --> 13:12.250
More like being taken off work.

13:12.580 --> 13:13.150
Alright.

13:13.450 --> 13:14.340
I got it.

13:30.270 --> 13:31.130
What happened?

13:33.460 --> 13:34.920
They've taken me off work.

13:35.780 --> 13:37.980
And I have to undergo an investigation.

13:39.870 --> 13:40.670
It's fine.

13:41.420 --> 13:42.950
My salary is pretty decent.

13:45.940 --> 13:47.150
Is that the point?

13:54.060 --> 13:55.260
You're pretty lucky.

13:55.830 --> 13:57.250
I'm not high-maintenance.

13:57.250 --> 13:58.580
I'm easy to take care of.

14:00.870 --> 14:01.750
I'm so lucky.

14:43.920 --> 14:44.790
Cheng is here.

14:45.710 --> 14:46.590
Cheng.

14:47.920 --> 14:49.510
How's that thing going, Cheng?

14:49.510 --> 14:51.510
Don't ask questions you shouldn't.

14:52.360 --> 14:53.550
It's handled.

14:54.480 --> 14:54.960
Here.

14:54.980 --> 14:56.060
Cheng, cheers.

15:49.390 --> 15:49.960
Liu.

16:07.470 --> 16:08.040
Come in.

16:14.960 --> 16:16.290
Leader Yao has arrived.

16:16.620 --> 16:18.480
He is in the task force office now.

16:18.920 --> 16:19.760
I see.

16:20.800 --> 16:22.260
You guys are close, right?

16:23.310 --> 16:23.910
We've met.

16:25.600 --> 16:28.360
You were at the
Provincial Crime Research Office before.

16:28.360 --> 16:31.270
You must have handled many major cases
with him.

16:31.670 --> 16:32.800
I'll head over then.

16:32.880 --> 16:34.210
Okay, you go ahead.

16:34.290 --> 16:35.750
Thanks for your hard work.

16:47.960 --> 16:49.760
The new boss has just taken over,

16:50.480 --> 16:51.880
and he's kicking you out.

16:54.160 --> 16:54.830
Sir.

16:55.670 --> 16:57.340
Don't kick me while I'm down.

16:59.200 --> 17:00.670
To tell you the truth,

17:01.150 --> 17:03.150
it was Leader Yao

17:03.480 --> 17:06.410
who fully supported you
to take on the Meng Ling case.

17:06.680 --> 17:08.280
Look at what you've done now.

17:08.480 --> 17:10.010
It's like a slap in his face.

17:11.270 --> 17:12.200
He knows me?

17:12.349 --> 17:13.700
Of course he does.

17:14.720 --> 17:15.800
He handled the 8.17 Case

17:15.800 --> 17:17.380
himself.

17:18.160 --> 17:25.550
[Task Force]

17:23.750 --> 17:24.310
Come in.

17:29.990 --> 17:34.530
[Yao Weihai,
the leader of 8.17 task force]

17:32.750 --> 17:33.720
It's really you.

17:35.750 --> 17:36.410
Leader Yao.

17:37.030 --> 17:37.890
Close the door.

17:48.930 --> 17:49.510
How is it?

17:49.700 --> 17:51.430
Are you getting used to it here?

17:51.970 --> 17:52.700
Pretty good.

17:54.020 --> 17:54.650
Hansheng,

17:55.320 --> 17:57.250
Mr. Wang went through a lot of trouble

17:57.250 --> 17:59.390
to get you that teaching job
at the University

17:59.390 --> 18:00.760
just to keep you safe.

18:01.640 --> 18:02.610
But you insist

18:02.640 --> 18:04.500
on getting involved in this case.

18:05.370 --> 18:07.830
Have you thought about
how big the risks are?

18:09.300 --> 18:09.700
Hiding

18:10.170 --> 18:11.430
is never the solution.

18:14.170 --> 18:15.900
If I hadn't come back this time,

18:16.380 --> 18:17.300
I would have never known

18:17.300 --> 18:18.720
you'd been at the Provincial Department

18:18.720 --> 18:20.130
the whole time.

18:21.620 --> 18:23.480
If you hadn't come back this time,

18:23.760 --> 18:25.090
I would have never known

18:25.340 --> 18:28.400
that you'd been investigating
the 8.17 Case all along.

18:32.860 --> 18:34.180
Mr. Wang was right.

18:34.860 --> 18:35.790
There's a kind of

18:35.830 --> 18:37.690
restrained ruthlessness in you.

18:38.790 --> 18:40.450
And that kind of ruthlessness

18:42.120 --> 18:43.580
makes people feel uneasy.

18:44.930 --> 18:45.930
Does Zhou Jin know

18:46.230 --> 18:48.020
that you are still a police officer

18:48.020 --> 18:50.110
of the Criminal Investigation Department,

18:50.110 --> 18:51.110
Professor Jiang?

18:52.720 --> 18:53.590
In Haizhou,

18:54.160 --> 18:55.420
only a few core members

18:56.220 --> 18:57.200
of the public security bureau

18:57.200 --> 18:58.660
know about this identity.

18:59.290 --> 19:00.890
Zhou Jin is not a core member.

19:01.310 --> 19:02.110
Is it possible

19:02.510 --> 19:03.580
that Leader Yao doesn't want me

19:03.580 --> 19:04.510
on the 8.17 case?

19:04.750 --> 19:06.310
No, why wouldn't he want me?

19:07.160 --> 19:07.920
Perhaps,

19:08.680 --> 19:10.140
I'm too eager to solve the case,

19:10.140 --> 19:11.070
or

19:11.300 --> 19:12.080
I'm not qualified enough,

19:12.080 --> 19:13.110
or I don't carry enough weight,

19:13.110 --> 19:14.510
or I'd let personal feelings get involved.

19:14.510 --> 19:16.130
Alright, stop guessing.

19:16.640 --> 19:17.590
He's a high-ranking leader.

19:17.590 --> 19:20.190
He doesn't have time
to think about you all day.

19:21.090 --> 19:22.420
Just go back and behave.

19:23.000 --> 19:24.110
Study that

19:24.510 --> 19:26.430
interrogation record carefully,

19:26.430 --> 19:27.830
and reflect on yourself.

19:28.480 --> 19:29.160
Sir,

19:29.880 --> 19:30.910
I don't want to be suspended.

19:30.910 --> 19:33.110
There are lots of things you don't want.

19:34.400 --> 19:35.860
Does it make a difference?

19:37.370 --> 19:37.900
Alright.

19:39.630 --> 19:40.450
It's almost

19:41.710 --> 19:43.180
August 17th.

19:44.070 --> 19:45.370
If you don't ask for leave,

19:45.370 --> 19:46.700
I'll approve it myself.

19:47.260 --> 19:48.990
Go back and visit your parents.

19:55.790 --> 19:56.850
I'll head out then.

20:01.750 --> 20:03.750
The situation is still unclear.

20:04.050 --> 20:05.600
For the sake of your safety,

20:07.960 --> 20:10.090
I don't want you involved in this case.

20:10.720 --> 20:11.570
If Mr. Wang

20:11.790 --> 20:12.400
knew,

20:12.880 --> 20:14.140
he would agree with me.

20:18.200 --> 20:19.460
Zhou Jin's suspension

20:20.110 --> 20:21.910
was also arranged by you, right?

20:23.960 --> 20:25.820
You are the head of the task force.

20:26.160 --> 20:27.920
I believe whatever you decide,

20:28.160 --> 20:29.560
you've got your reasons.

20:30.070 --> 20:31.800
But I also want to say something

20:31.830 --> 20:33.360
about my partner, Zhou Jin.

20:34.030 --> 20:35.110
Her ability

20:35.350 --> 20:36.590
got her into the CIB

20:37.160 --> 20:38.690
and onto the Meng Ling case.

20:44.000 --> 20:44.790
If it weren't for the major breakthrough

20:44.790 --> 20:45.880
in the 8.17 case,

20:46.510 --> 20:48.510
I believe you wouldn't have come back.

20:48.510 --> 20:50.310
However, before your next move,

20:51.030 --> 20:51.960
there is someone

20:52.400 --> 20:54.270
I think you should pay attention to.

20:54.270 --> 20:54.680
Who?

20:55.400 --> 20:56.130
Jiang Cheng.

20:56.960 --> 20:57.510
Why?

20:59.590 --> 21:01.350
Aren't you supposed to ask
who he is first?

21:01.350 --> 21:02.680
I've checked the files.

21:03.030 --> 21:04.350
He's He Wu's subordinate.

21:04.350 --> 21:05.550
He used to be a cop too.

21:05.960 --> 21:06.560
That's it.

21:09.380 --> 21:10.640
I think that's enough.

21:19.000 --> 21:19.730
How did it go?

21:20.070 --> 21:20.870
Done talking?

21:22.350 --> 21:23.200
I'm screwed.

21:23.860 --> 21:25.190
I really got suspended.

21:26.180 --> 21:27.510
You only got suspended.

21:27.800 --> 21:29.030
I was fired to my face.

21:29.680 --> 21:32.740
They won't let me assist
in the investigation anymore.

21:33.510 --> 21:34.570
What's the reason?

21:41.240 --> 21:43.440
It seems like ever since you married me,

21:43.740 --> 21:45.600
nothing good has happened to you.

21:50.830 --> 21:51.680
Marrying you

21:52.830 --> 21:55.760
is already the best thing
that's ever happened to me.

22:04.310 --> 22:05.170
Of course it is.

22:11.230 --> 22:13.360
Meng Ling's case is about to be closed.

22:13.690 --> 22:15.890
Chief Tan said he could give me time off.

22:16.440 --> 22:18.110
I want to go home to see my parents.

22:18.110 --> 22:19.310
Will you come with me?

22:20.570 --> 22:21.500
I'll go with you.

22:26.240 --> 22:27.900
But the leverage Meng Ling has

22:28.270 --> 22:29.590
over Lai San

22:29.880 --> 22:31.240
still remains unknown.

22:33.310 --> 22:34.160
And that gun.

22:36.180 --> 22:37.310
It's still missing.

22:40.240 --> 22:41.970
Everything will become clear.

23:23.120 --> 23:23.720
Mr. Jiang,

23:24.220 --> 23:24.750
please.

23:38.620 --> 23:39.350
You're here.

23:40.350 --> 23:40.750
Boss.

23:41.720 --> 23:42.330
Cheng.

23:44.200 --> 23:44.750
Ms. Qiu.

23:46.550 --> 23:47.110
Hello.

23:47.440 --> 23:48.040
I'm Qiu Ye.

23:49.200 --> 23:50.530
Hello. I'm Jiang Cheng.

23:55.880 --> 23:57.140
Don't you remember me,

23:57.660 --> 23:58.520
Officer Jiang?

24:04.160 --> 24:09.190
[2011]

24:04.470 --> 24:05.060
Freeze.

24:05.080 --> 24:05.850
Police.

24:06.030 --> 24:07.270
Don't move.

24:09.750 --> 24:10.350
Freeze.

24:13.960 --> 24:15.030
Hold them all down.

24:20.240 --> 24:21.030
Stand up.

24:24.000 --> 24:24.790
Stand up!

24:59.110 --> 25:00.440
Will I go to jail,

25:00.440 --> 25:01.550
Officer?

25:01.830 --> 25:02.690
Pregnant women

25:02.960 --> 25:04.750
usually serve their sentence
outside of prison.

25:04.750 --> 25:05.950
Don't touch it again.

25:06.310 --> 25:07.720
If not for yourself,

25:08.160 --> 25:09.960
do it for the child in your belly.

25:15.440 --> 25:17.840
It seems Officer Jiang still remembers me.

25:19.790 --> 25:20.550
Don't swear.

25:20.640 --> 25:21.700
Just call me Cheng.

25:22.450 --> 25:23.110
Okay.

25:24.680 --> 25:26.080
I haven't seen you in years,

25:26.080 --> 25:26.800
Ms...

25:27.160 --> 25:27.790
Qiu.

25:28.160 --> 25:29.690
You are still so beautiful.

25:30.560 --> 25:33.160
I've spent a lot of money
on my face these years.

25:33.880 --> 25:34.680
It's worth it.

25:34.790 --> 25:35.270
Really?

25:36.730 --> 25:38.000
Here, let's sit.

25:48.270 --> 25:48.960
Cheng,

25:49.790 --> 25:51.550
Lai Zhengtian is finished.

25:53.070 --> 25:54.000
I said

25:54.930 --> 25:56.390
I'd let you take his place,

25:57.070 --> 25:58.270
and I'll keep my word.

25:58.750 --> 25:59.810
From now on, Ms. Qiu

26:00.070 --> 26:01.070
is your resource.

26:06.270 --> 26:07.960
I wonder which part of the resources

26:07.960 --> 26:09.490
is Ms. Qiu responsible for?

26:11.350 --> 26:12.610
The unspeakable part.

26:15.600 --> 26:16.200
Boss,

26:16.810 --> 26:19.270
does that mean
I'm really entering the core?

26:19.790 --> 26:20.390
Of course.

26:20.640 --> 26:21.370
Absolutely.

26:26.070 --> 26:26.720
Ms. Qiu,

26:27.060 --> 26:29.260
I'll be counting on you then from now on.

26:30.350 --> 26:32.010
Don't get all polite just yet.

26:32.640 --> 26:35.200
There's something
I haven't had a chance to say yet.

26:35.200 --> 26:35.790
Boss He,

26:36.750 --> 26:39.350
you know the guns
that slipped from your hand?

26:39.650 --> 26:41.340
Old Scorpion isn't happy about that.

26:41.340 --> 26:43.200
That's why he sent me here

26:44.000 --> 26:45.550
to talk it over with you.

26:47.350 --> 26:48.280
What do you mean?

26:49.510 --> 26:51.320
The Hengyun Logistics channel

26:51.350 --> 26:52.950
will be shut down for a while.

26:53.490 --> 26:54.490
And all inventory

26:56.180 --> 26:57.180
will be recalled.

26:58.640 --> 26:59.750
When will it start?

27:06.440 --> 27:07.070
Now.

27:10.790 --> 27:11.450
The power's out!

27:11.450 --> 27:13.110
Go check the circuit breaker!

27:19.000 --> 27:19.790
Old Scorpion says

27:19.790 --> 27:21.920
he wants you to take a break for a while.

27:27.370 --> 27:28.500
Didn't you hear her?

27:29.590 --> 27:31.250
This comes from Old Scorpion.

27:39.760 --> 27:40.520
Thank you.

27:41.640 --> 27:44.240
If there's nothing else,
I'll be leaving then.

27:50.960 --> 27:51.550
Ms. Qiu.

27:59.030 --> 28:01.090
Please go back and tell Old Scorpion.

28:02.270 --> 28:03.240
No matter what,

28:04.720 --> 28:06.920
Haizhou still belongs to the He family.

28:09.150 --> 28:11.080
I'll make sure he gets the message.

28:39.880 --> 28:40.680
Where are we?

28:42.550 --> 28:43.680
Just got off the highway.

28:43.680 --> 28:44.880
There's still half an hour.

28:44.880 --> 28:46.410
You can get some more sleep.

28:49.930 --> 28:51.790
Do you want me to drive for a while?

28:52.000 --> 28:52.800
I'm not tired.

28:58.110 --> 28:58.920
What's wrong?

29:04.270 --> 29:05.530
For the last few years,

29:06.650 --> 29:08.650
whenever August 17th comes around,

29:09.640 --> 29:10.640
I come back.

29:12.590 --> 29:14.110
Always by myself.

29:14.830 --> 29:15.830
Walking this road

29:16.440 --> 29:17.640
alone.

29:20.200 --> 29:22.200
To be honest, I always feel a bit down

29:23.350 --> 29:24.590
around this time.

29:27.880 --> 29:29.480
You got suspended this year.

29:29.590 --> 29:31.120
Doesn't that make it worse?

29:31.790 --> 29:32.470
No.

29:34.000 --> 29:35.600
Because you're here with me.

29:39.550 --> 29:40.420
If we get home early,

29:40.420 --> 29:41.880
we can stay a few more days.

29:49.550 --> 29:50.590
Professor Jiang,

29:50.880 --> 29:52.550
you're quite good-looking.

29:55.110 --> 29:56.920
Did you marry me for my looks?

29:59.960 --> 30:00.920
Don't ask.

30:32.310 --> 30:34.480
I haven't been back to Zhizi Alley
in a long time.

30:34.480 --> 30:35.610
It's good to be back.

30:36.500 --> 30:38.030
After you moved away for high school,

30:38.030 --> 30:39.560
you never came back, right?

30:55.310 --> 30:56.400
There's an old man

30:57.270 --> 30:59.000
living in the Courtyard 23 now.

31:11.720 --> 31:12.590
Jin,

31:12.790 --> 31:14.160
you're back quite early this year.

31:14.160 --> 31:14.720
Bin,

31:14.720 --> 31:15.800
how many times have I told you?

31:15.800 --> 31:17.720
Don't ride that beat-up bike
around my alley.

31:17.720 --> 31:18.850
What beat-up bike?

31:19.270 --> 31:20.830
This is a a brand-name one, okay?

31:20.830 --> 31:23.690
People would steal its wheels
if I leave it outside.

31:24.520 --> 31:26.270
[Yan Bin,
the owner of Mr. Yan's hotpot restaurant]

31:25.440 --> 31:26.100
Who's this?

31:26.590 --> 31:27.550
He's...

31:28.310 --> 31:29.270
Look who's back!

31:29.270 --> 31:30.070
Mom.

31:32.000 --> 31:33.310
My precious daughter.

31:34.170 --> 31:35.760
I missed you.

31:37.240 --> 31:39.040
Why have you lost so much weight?

31:39.410 --> 31:41.310
You need to eat well,
no matter how busy you are.

31:41.310 --> 31:43.370
Your little body
can't take the strain anymore.

31:43.370 --> 31:44.520
I'm fine, really.

31:46.330 --> 31:47.520
Dad, is your leg better?

31:47.520 --> 31:48.430
Same as always.

31:49.680 --> 31:51.210
You've got more white hair.

31:51.520 --> 31:52.790
All my old friends

31:52.820 --> 31:54.480
have more white hair than I do.

31:55.550 --> 31:56.270
Hansheng,

31:56.420 --> 31:57.420
you must be tired.

31:57.960 --> 31:58.820
Not at all, Mom.

31:59.590 --> 32:00.310
Come in.

32:00.350 --> 32:01.210
Come in and sit.

32:01.240 --> 32:01.720
Right.

32:01.740 --> 32:02.260
I got it.

32:02.290 --> 32:03.030
I got it.

32:05.200 --> 32:06.200
Let's go in first.

32:06.550 --> 32:07.810
Bin, come on in with us.

32:08.790 --> 32:09.880
Nah, it's okay, Uncle.

32:09.880 --> 32:11.480
I just want to have a word with Jin.

32:11.480 --> 32:12.590
Sure. You two chat.

32:13.880 --> 32:14.640
Go ahead.

32:16.070 --> 32:17.270
You have a boyfriend?

32:18.360 --> 32:19.610
Tomorrow night, dinner time,

32:19.610 --> 32:20.480
we'll talk about it in detail then.

32:20.480 --> 32:21.860
Alright? I'm heading off now.

32:21.860 --> 32:22.860
Wait, wait, wait.

32:23.510 --> 32:25.000
Why does he look familiar?

32:28.060 --> 32:30.060
The young master from Courtyard 23?

32:31.790 --> 32:32.990
Right, right, right.

32:33.690 --> 32:34.720
Wait, wait, wait.

32:36.110 --> 32:36.830
Buns, buns.

32:37.180 --> 32:37.580
Buns.

32:37.600 --> 32:39.660
My mom told me to bring you these buns.

32:39.750 --> 32:40.830
Here.

32:41.200 --> 32:42.470
Is it stuffed
with preserved mustard greens?

32:42.470 --> 32:44.030
Just eat. Who cares what's inside?

32:44.030 --> 32:44.590
Mom.

32:45.830 --> 32:46.920
Buns.

32:56.850 --> 32:57.640
Brother.

32:58.400 --> 32:59.200
Jin has a boyfriend.

32:59.200 --> 33:00.460
Do you know about this?

33:01.400 --> 33:01.920
Here.

33:02.000 --> 33:02.730
Son-in-law,

33:03.070 --> 33:04.340
have another sip with me.

33:04.340 --> 33:05.350
Here's to you, Dad.

33:05.350 --> 33:05.880
Okay.

33:11.720 --> 33:12.480
It's been a long time

33:12.480 --> 33:14.270
since I had a drink this good.

33:16.000 --> 33:16.730
Come on, eat.

33:17.050 --> 33:18.660
Your mom's cooking is really good.

33:18.660 --> 33:19.590
It's delicious.

33:22.350 --> 33:22.960
Mom,

33:23.310 --> 33:24.680
what are you looking at?

33:24.880 --> 33:25.920
Your mom is looking at her son-in-law.

33:25.920 --> 33:28.250
The more she looks,
the more she likes him.

33:29.190 --> 33:30.130
You silly girl,

33:30.160 --> 33:31.440
you're really lucky.

33:32.550 --> 33:33.750
Hansheng, this is your first time here.

33:33.750 --> 33:35.550
Let me know if you need anything.

33:36.070 --> 33:37.470
Everything's fine, Mom.

33:38.160 --> 33:38.830
Hansheng,

33:38.830 --> 33:39.830
you don't have to peel them for me.

33:39.830 --> 33:40.920
I can do it myself.

33:41.340 --> 33:41.820
Here.

33:45.000 --> 33:45.860
By the way, Mom.

33:46.310 --> 33:47.200
Hansheng

33:47.240 --> 33:49.300
is used to using serving chopsticks.

33:49.390 --> 33:50.020
Okay, okay.

33:50.020 --> 33:50.750
No need, Mom.

33:51.000 --> 33:52.800
There's no need for that at home.

33:55.590 --> 33:57.640
Hansheng has been to our house before,

33:57.640 --> 33:58.310
right?

33:59.510 --> 34:00.110
Has he?

34:00.680 --> 34:01.640
Do you remember?

34:02.240 --> 34:03.880
When Jin was little,

34:03.900 --> 34:05.430
she brought Hansheng home.

34:05.680 --> 34:06.400
I remember.

34:06.880 --> 34:09.080
The two little kids were holding hands.

34:10.590 --> 34:11.800
When did that happen?

34:12.710 --> 34:13.639
Do you remember?

34:14.920 --> 34:17.030
What I remember most is that woman.

34:17.520 --> 34:18.980
The nanny from your house.

34:19.020 --> 34:21.550
She was taking care of you
and a few other kids.

34:22.320 --> 34:23.520
You were all victims.

34:23.820 --> 34:25.230
Later, she got arrested,

34:25.250 --> 34:27.190
and spent two or three years in prison.

34:27.190 --> 34:28.190
Nanny?

34:28.590 --> 34:29.670
Arrested?

34:30.480 --> 34:32.880
You were the one
who first found out about it.

34:32.880 --> 34:34.880
And then you brought Hansheng here.

34:35.710 --> 34:37.030
It's normal she doesn't remember.

34:37.030 --> 34:38.940
Back then,
she was always bringing people home.

34:38.940 --> 34:39.830
We were so busy.

34:39.860 --> 34:40.880
Dad, what are you talking about?

34:40.880 --> 34:42.940
Who was always bringing people home?

34:43.590 --> 34:45.840
Maybe it was that fever.

34:46.219 --> 34:47.150
It fried her brain.

34:47.150 --> 34:48.070
So she lost her memory.

34:48.070 --> 34:49.280
What are you talking about?

34:49.280 --> 34:50.320
It's true.

34:50.659 --> 34:52.920
That night,
I told her to go home with you.

34:53.000 --> 34:54.510
But she wouldn't let go of me.

34:54.510 --> 34:56.590
She insisted on going to find him
in the rain.

34:56.590 --> 34:59.070
Then she got soaked
and came down with a fever the next day.

34:59.070 --> 35:00.070
She was all dazed.

35:00.320 --> 35:01.110
That's true.

35:02.270 --> 35:03.460
Do you remember now?

35:04.990 --> 35:06.150
How old was I?

35:06.470 --> 35:07.730
When you were in elementary school.

35:07.730 --> 35:09.060
You were only this tall.

35:09.290 --> 35:10.420
Elementary school?

35:13.480 --> 35:14.810
Do you really remember?

35:16.530 --> 35:18.860
You even wanted
to steal a meatball for me.

35:27.760 --> 35:32.740
[1997]

35:28.210 --> 35:29.870
Do you want some shrimp chips?

35:35.570 --> 35:37.050
They're so good.

35:41.870 --> 35:43.430
You don't like them?

35:46.600 --> 35:47.830
My mom said

35:48.800 --> 35:50.730
I can't have snacks before dinner.

35:52.020 --> 35:53.080
Aren't you hungry?

35:58.850 --> 36:00.750
Wait here,
I'll steal a big meatball for you.

36:00.750 --> 36:02.210
Meatballs aren't snacks.

36:28.360 --> 36:29.800
Here, drink some tea.

36:51.030 --> 36:51.760
Hansheng,

36:53.720 --> 36:54.680
thank you.

36:57.880 --> 36:58.510
Dad,

36:59.250 --> 37:00.650
I should be thanking you.

37:03.840 --> 37:05.170
You finally brought him home.

37:05.170 --> 37:06.740
I'm finally relieved.

37:08.110 --> 37:09.370
Are you happy with him?

37:09.590 --> 37:11.520
What matters is that you're happy.

37:12.590 --> 37:13.510
Back then,

37:13.800 --> 37:15.400
it was so hard

37:15.510 --> 37:17.310
to get you to go on a date with him.

37:20.190 --> 37:20.710
Look,

37:21.400 --> 37:23.660
he's got a lot to talk about
with your dad.

37:25.150 --> 37:27.010
He teaches Criminal Psychology.

37:27.190 --> 37:29.450
He's very popular with old cops like Dad.

37:30.760 --> 37:31.510
Jin.

37:31.840 --> 37:32.920
Busy as you are,

37:33.030 --> 37:34.960
you still need to have a wedding.

37:36.320 --> 37:39.180
You can't keep making Hansheng
compromise for you.

37:40.050 --> 37:42.650
Let's just get through
this busy period first.

37:43.590 --> 37:45.030
For the wedding,

37:45.110 --> 37:47.440
you need to notify the parents and elders.

37:47.790 --> 37:49.300
You can't just decide on your own.

37:49.300 --> 37:50.900
I know. We will.

37:57.130 --> 37:58.930
If your brother were still here,

37:59.400 --> 38:01.260
he'd definitely be happy for you.

38:05.550 --> 38:06.920
He definitely would be.

38:57.870 --> 39:03.350
♪ Win like this, lose like this ♪

39:03.380 --> 39:07.350
♪ Don't mock others' greed and obsession ♪

39:08.310 --> 39:11.750
♪ Grievances and joys are hard to let go ♪

39:11.770 --> 39:13.920
♪ Between heaven and earth ♪

39:13.940 --> 39:16.890
♪ Carefree like this ♪

39:16.920 --> 39:18.430
♪ In a snap of fingers ♪

39:18.450 --> 39:22.800
♪ Time passes like this ♪

39:22.820 --> 39:26.730
♪ You're like this, I'm like this ♪

39:27.470 --> 39:31.110
♪ A sword in hand and a ruler in heart ♪

39:31.140 --> 39:36.270
♪ Let go of ego and place the chess ♪

39:36.300 --> 39:39.060
♪ Dancing with the sword ♪

39:39.090 --> 39:41.460
♪ Writing with the brush ♪

39:41.480 --> 39:43.880
♪ In the unseen ♪

39:43.900 --> 39:46.050
♪ Each one has his own gift ♪

39:56.070 --> 39:56.920
This is?

39:58.780 --> 39:59.910
This is my brother's

40:00.870 --> 40:02.100
favorite song.

40:04.670 --> 40:05.550
Those...

40:06.580 --> 40:09.180
are all the cassettes
my brother bought for me.

40:10.220 --> 40:11.300
People these days

40:12.800 --> 40:15.200
don't seem to listen to cassettes anymore.

40:17.510 --> 40:20.590
Cassettes feel so old-fashioned.

40:22.840 --> 40:25.100
It's like some things from my childhood.

40:27.480 --> 40:29.030
They feel so far away.

40:30.360 --> 40:32.550
I don't even seem to remember them.

40:33.880 --> 40:35.360
But there are others

40:38.480 --> 40:39.960
I remember very clearly.

40:41.920 --> 40:43.850
And when I think of them sometimes,

40:44.760 --> 40:46.070
I feel a little sad.

40:49.030 --> 40:50.630
Jiang Hansheng, do you know?

40:52.030 --> 40:53.150
Actually,

40:56.500 --> 40:57.500
Zhizi Alley

40:58.260 --> 41:00.140
is a place I'm afraid of.

41:02.060 --> 41:03.520
I really want to come back,

41:05.910 --> 41:07.200
but I'm so scared.

41:17.710 --> 41:19.070
If I take one more step,

41:20.010 --> 41:22.810
I'll be the farthest away
from home I've ever been.

41:25.030 --> 41:26.890
It's from "The Lord of the Rings."

41:29.570 --> 41:31.300
As long as the case gets solved,

41:32.670 --> 41:34.130
I don't care how many steps

41:34.670 --> 41:35.550
I have to take.

41:37.670 --> 41:38.710
I'm just afraid

41:40.670 --> 41:42.110
I won't have the chance.

41:43.880 --> 41:44.710
You will.

41:50.840 --> 41:52.700
What song do you want to listen to?

41:52.770 --> 41:53.900
I'll play it for you.

41:55.460 --> 41:57.060
I like songs without lyrics.

41:59.320 --> 42:00.720
Lyrics disturb the mind.

42:00.720 --> 42:03.060
They create strong
psychological suggestions,

42:03.060 --> 42:05.190
or even self-fulfilling prophecies.

42:09.480 --> 42:10.410
Am I being weird?

42:14.360 --> 42:16.420
You lived next door when we were kids.

42:17.420 --> 42:18.340
Why

42:19.800 --> 42:21.330
didn't I ever play with you?

42:23.530 --> 42:25.050
Maybe because I was weird.

42:26.180 --> 42:28.380
Being weird means you're interesting.

42:28.570 --> 42:30.230
I was the one who didn't get it.

42:31.860 --> 42:32.900
I'm sorry.

42:33.230 --> 42:35.510
The bed here isn't as big
as the one at our home.

42:35.510 --> 42:36.710
Can you get used to it?

42:37.150 --> 42:37.800
Yes, I can.
